You can use the following things in your prompt :

   $hp -> Your hitpoints
   $sp -> Your spellpoints
   $ep -> Your endurance points
   $maxhp -> Your max hp
   $maxsp -> Your max sp
   $maxep -> Your max ep
   $level -> Your level
   $time  -> Current time

 Example : prompt Hp: ($hp/$maxhp) >
           prompt clear  (CLEAR your prompt)
